msgid ""
"Those of you who follow the desktop Linux news will know that\n"
"upstream [MATE Desktop recently released version 1.24](https://mate-desktop."
"org/blog/2020-02-10-mate-1-24-released/).\n"
"Ubuntu MATE 20.04 is shipping with MATE Desktop 1.24. Thus, all of the\n"
"improvements in MATE Desktop 1.24 are present in Ubuntu MATE 20.04 LTS."
msgstr ""
"Ceux d'entre vous qui suivent l'actualité du bureau Linux sauront qu'en "
"amont le [Bureau MATE est récemment sorti en version 1.24](https://mate-"
"desktop.org/blog/2020-02-10-mate-1-24-released/).\n"
"Ubuntu MATE 20.04 est fourni avec le Bureau MATE 1.24. Ainsi, toutes\n"
